<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 center-block">
      <h2 class="welcome-message"><strong>Welcome <%= current_user.first_name %></strong></h2>
      <p>All the DPSST deliveries for this winter and spring have been loaded. Not all of them have been scheduled but you can checkout the details we have so far</p>
      <% if current_user.instructor? %>
        <% if !current_user.deliveries.nil? %>
          <h3><strong>Your Deliveries</strong></h3>
          <ul>
          <% current_user.deliveries.each do |d| %>
          <%= link_to delivery_path(d) do %>
            <li><%= d.course.course_number %>  â€“  <%= d.course.title %>  |  <%= d.start_date.try(:strftime, "%b %e") %> - <%= d.end_date.try(:strftime, "%b %e, %Y") %>  |  <%= display_location(d) %></li>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
          </ul>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>

      <br>
      <h3><strong>App Todo</strong></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Add lead and unit quals to instructor so only qualifed users show when assigning instructor to delivery.</li>
        <li>Add file upload so that each delivery can store files such as fliers and welcome letters.</li>
        <li>Restrict authorization so only admin can create or modify a Course.</li>
        <li>Add some compelling content to home page instead of this list :)</li>
      </ul>
      <h3><strong>Issues</strong></h3>
      <p>If you have any suggestions or find any bugs shoot me an email at bwoodreid@gmail.com.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
